channel.description: I downloaded a blank source because i want to make a perfect runescape duplicate back from like 2006 well when i open up the source i have a teleport.cfg i'm trying to make the teleports first how do i make it so it recognizes the teleport.cfg for the teleports

item.title: Teleports
item.dc:creator: @GrimReapersScythe GrimReapersScythe
item.description:
@GrimReapersScythe wrote:

The teleports don’t load from a config file. If there is a teleport.cfg, it’s probably loading runes to use for the teleports. To change teleports, search in clickingmost.java, or client.java.
